WEBVTT

00:11.960 --> 00:12.750
This letter

00:13.750 --> 00:17.350
is the distress letter Consort Virtue
wrote to Wei Yan years ago.

00:17.600 --> 00:19.640
Wei Yan, for his own selfish desires,

00:19.640 --> 00:21.900
returned to the Capital without orders.

00:21.920 --> 00:24.640
He abandoned the soldiers of Jinzhou
at the front line,

00:24.640 --> 00:25.500
and ultimately

00:25.600 --> 00:26.860
caused a catastrophe.

00:27.250 --> 00:27.960
[Yan, I hope this letter finds you well.
Disaster has struck, and I seek your help.]

00:27.990 --> 00:28.800
[Beijue has invaded our Great Yin.
My father led the troops]

00:28.820 --> 00:29.820
[to protect the peace of our court.
But it was all the schemes of traitors.]

00:29.850 --> 00:30.470
[They conspired and slandered, and that
foolish ruler easily believed them.]

00:32.520 --> 00:34.070
A thief crying "thief".

00:35.520 --> 00:36.240
Wei Yan,

00:37.880 --> 00:40.810
you are the biggest traitor
in the Battle of Jinzhou!

00:41.520 --> 00:43.120
This is Qi Rongyin's letter.

00:43.270 --> 00:44.420
It's been 17 years.

00:44.750 --> 00:46.150
You must have forgotten.

00:47.200 --> 00:48.400
Let me read it for you.

00:49.520 --> 00:50.350
Yan.

00:50.790 --> 00:53.190
-May this letter remind you of me.
-Shut up!

00:53.560 --> 00:55.750
Wei Changyu,
if you want a fight, let's fight.

00:55.750 --> 00:58.300
Don't insult the innocence of the deceased.

01:00.650 --> 01:03.390
Prime Minister Wei, it seems there are
still people you care about.

01:03.390 --> 01:04.640
Seventeen years ago,

01:05.710 --> 01:07.200
my mother hid this letter

01:08.030 --> 01:10.280
inside the candy box you gave her.

01:11.300 --> 01:12.230
All these years,

01:13.150 --> 01:14.430
you've done too much evil.

01:14.430 --> 01:16.030
That's why you felt so guilty

01:16.039 --> 01:18.370
and didn't dare touch the candy box at all.

01:19.000 --> 01:20.920
Prime Minister Wei, dare I ask you,

01:20.920 --> 01:22.050
in the past 17 years,

01:23.039 --> 01:25.039
have you ever repented to my father?

01:25.660 --> 01:26.870
Have you ever pitied

01:27.760 --> 01:29.560
the thousands of dead soldiers?

01:30.000 --> 01:31.200
Have you ever mourned

01:31.680 --> 01:34.210
your sister who was forced to commit suicide?

01:36.280 --> 01:37.640
A fake letter,

01:38.200 --> 01:39.870
a pair of fake Tiger Tally,

01:40.070 --> 01:41.950
and you want to smear me?

01:43.710 --> 01:45.680
Haven't you silenced enough people

01:45.680 --> 01:47.039
because of this letter?

01:48.070 --> 01:49.840
If Consort Virtue knew in the afterlife

01:49.840 --> 01:51.710
-the things you've done...
-Shut up!

01:51.710 --> 01:52.770
Don't mention her.

01:58.350 --> 02:00.950
It's not hard to prove if the Tiger Tally

02:01.430 --> 02:02.150
is real.

02:02.680 --> 02:04.280
The Tiger Tally is a treasure of the state,

02:04.280 --> 02:06.080
archived in the Ministry of War.

02:06.230 --> 02:08.229
Although the archives were burned,

02:08.240 --> 02:10.190
the person who made the Tiger Tally back then,

02:10.190 --> 02:12.360
Grand Tutor Tao, is still alive.

02:13.030 --> 02:15.490
Prime Minister Wei, you just need to ask him.

02:16.970 --> 02:19.370
Grand Tutor Tao has arrived.

02:26.000 --> 02:28.180
Greetings, Your Majesty.

02:28.280 --> 02:29.060
Rise.

02:29.800 --> 02:31.240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

02:32.150 --> 02:35.450
Grand Tutor Tao is one of the few
witnesses from that time.

02:35.760 --> 02:38.290
We must preserve the Royal Family's dignity.

02:38.430 --> 02:40.310
As such, please determine if this

02:40.310 --> 02:42.120
military tally is genuine or not.

02:42.120 --> 02:43.520
Yes, Your Majesty.

02:52.450 --> 02:53.620
[Talisman of Military Field]

02:58.510 --> 02:59.770
Your Majesty,

02:59.970 --> 03:03.500
I personally supervised the making
of this tally back then.

03:04.310 --> 03:06.320
There is a mark on it.

03:07.030 --> 03:09.290
This is the real item.

03:11.900 --> 03:13.030
Prime Minister Wei,

03:14.330 --> 03:15.980
what else do you have to say?

03:25.630 --> 03:27.430
You will be Empress soon.

03:31.560 --> 03:32.190
Wei Yan!

03:32.800 --> 03:34.190
You are ambitious, cruel,

03:34.190 --> 03:35.240
and have deceived your ruler.

03:35.240 --> 03:36.770
Your crimes deserve death!

03:37.079 --> 03:38.010
Imperial Guard!

03:38.030 --> 03:38.520
Here.

03:38.630 --> 03:39.630
Take him down.

03:39.710 --> 03:40.310
Yes.

04:00.470 --> 04:01.560
Wei Yan, you...

04:04.840 --> 04:06.380
Kid of the Qi family,

04:07.150 --> 04:08.910
do you have the guts?

04:12.000 --> 04:14.580
Yigui, you cannot make more mistakes.

04:22.800 --> 04:23.560
Report!

04:25.000 --> 04:26.170
Your Majesty, bad news.

04:26.170 --> 04:29.400
[Diligent and Virtuous]

04:26.510 --> 04:27.800
The rebel Sui Yuanhuai

04:27.800 --> 04:30.040
has sent his army to breach the Great Yin Gate.

04:30.040 --> 04:30.800
What?

04:34.920 --> 04:36.350
How did they get in?

04:41.770 --> 04:43.390
The day has finally come.

04:45.000 --> 04:47.000
He certainly knows how to pick a day.

04:53.120 --> 04:55.580
The grievance between us, uncle and nephew,

04:55.600 --> 04:56.870
must be settled.

04:57.760 --> 04:59.400
But before that,

05:00.040 --> 05:01.970
I must quell this rebellion first.

05:03.690 --> 05:04.370
Let's go.

06:35.690 --> 06:40.980
[Pursuit of Jade]

06:41.080 --> 06:43.659
[Episode 39]

06:44.750 --> 06:45.920
Everyone,

06:46.630 --> 06:47.680
kill them!

06:57.850 --> 07:02.890
[Great Yin Gate]

07:31.440 --> 07:34.040
Welcome the rightful owner back to the palace.

07:34.870 --> 07:37.470
Welcome the rightful owner back to the palace.

07:37.570 --> 07:40.170
Welcome the rightful owner back to the palace.

07:40.480 --> 07:43.080
Welcome the rightful owner back to the palace.

08:05.190 --> 08:07.790
Welcome the rightful owner back to the palace.

08:15.630 --> 08:16.830
After 17 years,

08:17.390 --> 08:20.120
I have finally reclaimed my rightful place.

08:23.680 --> 08:25.720
Your Highness regaining the throne

08:25.720 --> 08:27.700
is clearly the will of Heaven.

08:27.750 --> 08:29.390
It is your destiny.

08:29.560 --> 08:31.290
It is your destiny.

08:36.909 --> 08:37.720
Qianqian.

08:39.840 --> 08:40.750
Well?

08:41.630 --> 08:43.000
I have kept

08:44.240 --> 08:45.240
my promise to you.

08:46.000 --> 08:47.240
You madman.

08:49.440 --> 08:51.900
Do you really think I want to be your Empress?

08:52.790 --> 08:53.840
Keep dreaming.

09:01.520 --> 09:02.810
You will agree.

09:14.440 --> 09:15.300
Brother Sheng.

09:16.550 --> 09:19.240
You've sat on this throne for over a decade.

09:20.670 --> 09:22.200
Was it comfortable?

09:38.360 --> 09:39.150
Brother.

09:40.080 --> 09:40.630
I...

09:43.320 --> 09:45.650
I have been waiting for you for a long time.

09:46.910 --> 09:48.370
The Imperial Seal is here.

09:50.040 --> 09:51.260
It's all yours.

10:04.790 --> 10:07.150
Please don't kill me, Brother.

10:08.310 --> 10:09.730
Brother, don't kill me.

10:12.650 --> 10:15.790
To think Great Yin
has a pushover like you as the emperor...

10:15.790 --> 10:19.320
How can you live up to the torture
I've suffered all these years?

10:27.630 --> 10:28.430
Take him away.

10:28.910 --> 10:29.970
Await my judgment.

10:30.770 --> 10:31.440
Yes.

10:33.480 --> 10:34.280
Don't kill me.

10:35.360 --> 10:36.160
Don't kill me.

10:36.750 --> 10:37.550
Don't kill me.

10:41.390 --> 10:42.190
Don't kill me.

10:46.480 --> 10:48.600
Is he really going to be the Emperor?

10:51.270 --> 10:53.510
Report!
Unusual movements spotted at Xuan Gate.

10:53.510 --> 10:56.710
Reinforcements may be arriving
from outside the palace.

11:28.390 --> 11:29.030
Not good.

11:29.590 --> 11:30.490
It's a trap.

11:36.740 --> 11:40.560
Li Xing colluded with the rebel
Sui Yuanhuai to commit treason.

11:41.270 --> 11:43.560
Such traitors

11:43.840 --> 11:46.620
must all be arrested.

11:47.750 --> 11:48.960
Old Wretch Wei.

11:49.200 --> 11:50.490
Do not think

11:50.550 --> 11:52.400
that with just these few men,

11:52.750 --> 11:55.270
you can stop His Highness's Fifth Barracks.

12:14.510 --> 12:15.920
Is this not enough?

12:17.360 --> 12:18.770
Just these few men?

12:20.150 --> 12:22.660
Besides, it's not yet certain whose side

12:22.750 --> 12:24.360
Marquis of Wu'an is on.

12:26.280 --> 12:29.310
Marquis of Wu'an,
since you've come to join the fun,

12:29.730 --> 12:31.380
why not cooperate with me?

12:32.250 --> 12:35.060
I have already detained that puppet emperor.

12:35.750 --> 12:37.240
Why not serve me?

12:37.440 --> 12:40.440
After all, I am the true blood
of Crown Prince Chengde.

12:43.030 --> 12:43.960
Qi Min.

12:44.670 --> 12:46.670
You secretly colluded with Beijue

12:46.840 --> 12:49.840
and intended to use this chance
to threaten Great Yin.

12:49.840 --> 12:51.770
Did you really think I was unaware?

12:52.240 --> 12:54.270
Ever since you claimed to be
the heir of Crown Prince Chengde,

12:54.270 --> 12:55.510
you have forgotten the former Eastern Palace's

12:55.510 --> 12:58.200
bravery in swearing death
rather than surrendering to Beijue.

12:58.200 --> 12:59.500
How could I, Xie Zheng,

12:59.600 --> 13:01.200
ever submit to you?

13:01.270 --> 13:02.510
What?

13:04.750 --> 13:07.020
You dare to collude with Beijue in secret

13:07.270 --> 13:10.240
and hand over Great Yin's territory to barbarians?

13:10.910 --> 13:12.510
There is no turning back now.

13:13.240 --> 13:16.320
Grand Tutor Li, it is too late for regrets.

13:16.320 --> 13:16.790
You...

13:18.280 --> 13:22.050
What Prime Minister Wei has done
is far worse than what I have done.

13:23.030 --> 13:24.080
The fall of Jinzhou,

13:24.080 --> 13:25.810
the slaughter of its citizens,

13:26.200 --> 13:29.480
and the cession of the 12 commanderies
of Liaodong to the barbarians

13:29.480 --> 13:31.170
were all caused by Wei Yan

13:31.480 --> 13:34.550
in his desire to seize control of Great Yin.

13:35.150 --> 13:37.670
I am merely completing the game

13:37.670 --> 13:39.600
that he left unfinished years ago.

13:39.610 --> 13:40.210
You...

13:44.840 --> 13:45.970
Prime Minister Wei.

13:47.020 --> 13:48.670
Seventeen years ago,

13:49.030 --> 13:50.790
you bathed the palace in blood.

13:51.240 --> 13:53.570
Did you think that no one would know

13:53.720 --> 13:56.260
about your illicit affairs in the palace that way?

13:56.260 --> 13:58.930
You're just a bastard posing as royalty.

13:59.630 --> 14:03.500
How dare you spout nonsense
and fabricate facts?

14:03.870 --> 14:05.400
You know better than anyone

14:05.790 --> 14:08.750
who is spouting the nonsense here.

14:10.240 --> 14:11.240
Seize him.

14:11.870 --> 14:14.580
All the traitors and rebels present today

14:14.840 --> 14:16.720
shall be executed without mercy.

14:27.910 --> 14:29.840
Look, Prime Minister Wei.

14:30.440 --> 14:31.900
Your wife and son are here.

14:32.120 --> 14:33.290
I assure you,

14:33.390 --> 14:35.260
if your men dare to step forward,

14:35.360 --> 14:37.200
their heads will roll.

14:49.080 --> 14:51.460
I did not expect you to be so cold-blooded.

14:51.860 --> 14:53.380
Then let Madam Wei

14:53.750 --> 14:55.090
and the Young Master

14:55.550 --> 14:57.240
go to hell first.

15:14.390 --> 15:15.480
Kill them!

15:15.630 --> 15:16.480
Kill!

15:17.090 --> 15:20.860
Kill!

15:32.840 --> 15:33.760
Don't kill me.

15:33.910 --> 15:34.710
Don't kill me.

15:34.720 --> 15:35.640
Don't kill me.

15:36.320 --> 15:37.200
Don't kill me.

15:37.200 --> 15:38.070
Don't kill me.

15:38.090 --> 15:40.200
I will make you Great Generals, alright?

15:40.200 --> 15:40.870
Alright?

15:41.280 --> 15:44.140
One more word and you're dead,
you dog of an Emperor!

15:45.550 --> 15:47.410
It's time to end this.

15:48.360 --> 15:49.290
Prime Minister.

15:51.200 --> 15:53.430
This is between us, uncle and nephew.

15:55.510 --> 15:57.160
Stay out of it. Stand down.

16:33.510 --> 16:37.300
♪ The world is vast ♪

16:38.790 --> 16:44.780
♪ The storm is rising ♪

16:46.480 --> 16:50.780
♪ Day and night ♪

16:51.940 --> 16:55.630
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

16:56.910 --> 16:59.440
Your swordsmanship has improved quite a bit.

16:59.660 --> 17:03.870
♪ All people ♪

17:00.440 --> 17:02.500
I will use my father's swordsmanship

17:02.920 --> 17:05.079
to seek justice for my and Changyu's parents,

17:05.079 --> 17:10.550
♪ Are part of the past ♪

17:05.510 --> 17:08.530
the former Eastern Palace,
and the soldiers who died tragically

17:08.530 --> 17:09.690
in Jinzhou.

17:11.349 --> 17:12.240
Very well.

17:12.660 --> 17:17.589
♪ What's the date today? ♪

17:13.160 --> 17:13.960
Come on.

17:18.020 --> 17:24.750
♪ How lamentable ♪

17:39.950 --> 17:43.740
♪ The world is vast ♪

17:42.400 --> 17:43.490
Give up.

17:44.200 --> 17:45.640
You will never get

17:45.230 --> 17:51.340
♪ The storm is rising ♪

17:46.030 --> 17:47.560
what doesn't belong to you.

17:52.920 --> 17:55.040
Look, this empire belongs to me.

17:53.030 --> 17:57.300
♪ Day and night ♪

17:55.590 --> 17:57.110
It was mine from the start!

17:58.380 --> 18:02.110
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

17:59.640 --> 18:00.590
Do you like it?

18:01.480 --> 18:02.550
Do you?

18:04.350 --> 18:06.310
I don't want any of it.

18:06.100 --> 18:10.370
♪ All people ♪

18:11.070 --> 18:13.690
Being an emperor is hard.

18:11.770 --> 18:17.230
♪ Are part of the past ♪

18:19.100 --> 18:24.160
♪ What's the date today? ♪

18:22.440 --> 18:24.530
I don't want to be an emperor anymore.

18:24.460 --> 18:32.330
♪ How lamentable ♪

18:25.730 --> 18:27.670
I won't do it anymore.

18:35.750 --> 18:37.300
You really are mad!

18:37.590 --> 18:38.750
I am not mad.

18:39.880 --> 18:42.340
I chose to live because of you.

18:42.400 --> 18:43.400
For me?

18:44.960 --> 18:45.590
Fine.

18:46.920 --> 18:48.650
If I die, you'll stop being mad.

18:53.200 --> 18:55.480
I will not allow you to die.

18:58.070 --> 18:58.880
Qi Min!

18:59.280 --> 19:00.410
Let go of Qianqian.

19:02.110 --> 19:02.720
Changyu.

19:03.630 --> 19:04.830
Don't worry about me.

19:05.510 --> 19:06.740
I can't escape.

19:36.200 --> 19:37.450
Let go of her!

19:37.720 --> 19:38.920
Or I'll kill you.

19:41.070 --> 19:41.790
Changyu.

19:42.590 --> 19:43.590
Just let go.

19:44.550 --> 19:46.950
My matter with him shouldn't drag you down.

19:50.680 --> 19:52.120
I wanted imperial power.

19:52.920 --> 19:53.850
And I wanted you.

19:55.400 --> 19:56.310
But in the end,

19:57.200 --> 19:58.650
I have nothing.

19:58.830 --> 20:00.170
Let go!

20:00.200 --> 20:01.830
You'll kill her!

20:07.230 --> 20:08.650
He won't let go.

20:13.000 --> 20:15.210
He will never learn to let go.

20:13.360 --> 20:14.890
♪ I just don't want to ♪

20:15.750 --> 20:16.600
♪ Keep weighing every word ♪

20:16.620 --> 20:18.530
♪ And hiding in time in silence ♪

20:19.600 --> 20:21.340
♪ It's not that I don't believe in karma ♪

20:22.210 --> 20:24.120
♪ That I'm being stubborn ♪

20:24.590 --> 20:25.650
You're selfish,

20:25.840 --> 20:27.590
♪ Some endings have long been ♪

20:25.880 --> 20:26.850
cruel,

20:27.030 --> 20:28.150
and unpredictable.

20:28.150 --> 20:29.680
♪ Weathered through a thousand years ♪

20:28.960 --> 20:30.910
But all of this is your disguise.

20:29.710 --> 20:31.590
♪ Traced by those who come after ♪

20:31.550 --> 20:33.690
You're just hiding your fear.

20:32.000 --> 20:34.080
♪ Compared to fading away in sorrow ♪

20:34.560 --> 20:36.820
♪ I'd rather fight ♪

20:35.130 --> 20:36.530
You are a pitiful person.

20:37.440 --> 20:38.920
Is my love so worthless

20:37.470 --> 20:40.180
♪ Life's bitterness ♪

20:39.400 --> 20:40.860
that you can just trample on it?

20:40.560 --> 20:43.080
♪ Comes from love ♪

20:41.270 --> 20:42.350
That isn't love.

20:42.920 --> 20:44.830
It's possession. It's control!

20:43.990 --> 20:46.540
♪ Love, yet so hard to hold ♪

20:46.270 --> 20:47.850
I don't want anything.

20:47.100 --> 20:49.930
♪ Like holding a torch in the wilderness ♪

20:48.720 --> 20:50.350
I just want to leave you forever.

20:50.350 --> 20:52.570
♪ Time sings a mournful song ♪

20:53.410 --> 20:55.440
♪ Gathered little yet parted often ♪

20:55.950 --> 20:56.670
For you,

20:56.430 --> 20:59.500
♪ Just as tears fall into the long river ♪

20:59.160 --> 21:00.510
I'm willing to learn it once.

20:59.980 --> 21:04.970
♪ I must dive into the starry stream ♪

21:06.720 --> 21:07.390
♪ Don't mind me ♪

21:07.420 --> 21:08.480
♪ Everything has happened ♪

21:08.760 --> 21:12.230
♪ A thousand years from now
no one's blood will remain warm ♪

21:12.880 --> 21:14.960
♪ Let them laugh and mock ♪

21:15.350 --> 21:18.440
♪ As long as you remember me ♪

21:19.240 --> 21:19.810
♪ Forget about ♪

21:19.830 --> 21:21.060
♪ Leaving a name in history ♪

21:21.640 --> 21:24.750
♪ I only want to leave a mark
in your life ♪

21:25.550 --> 21:27.000
♪ I will let go ♪

21:27.980 --> 21:31.310
♪ After taking this one last gamble ♪

21:31.920 --> 21:32.490
♪ Forget about ♪

21:32.510 --> 21:33.700
♪ The carved stones or constellations ♪

21:34.260 --> 21:37.250
♪ I'll cast all karma behind me ♪

21:38.130 --> 21:40.160
♪ Beacon fires stir the lords ♪

21:40.530 --> 21:44.500
♪ Unstoppable, ruthless fate ♪

23:02.750 --> 23:04.310
Xuan!

23:05.350 --> 23:06.640
Xuan!

23:07.880 --> 23:09.010
This arrow

23:10.960 --> 23:14.020
is to repay you for saving my mother.

23:14.040 --> 23:15.640
Xuan!

23:18.160 --> 23:19.070
My father

23:19.830 --> 23:22.350
is not a bastard like you.

23:29.340 --> 23:30.420
Xuan!

24:10.890 --> 24:17.480
[Xie]

24:13.890 --> 24:16.090
The Jizhou and Xie Armies have arrived.

24:16.470 --> 24:17.670
The palace is secure.

24:18.070 --> 24:19.830
Soldiers who followed
Qi and Wei in rebellion,

24:19.830 --> 24:20.880
listen to me.

24:21.440 --> 24:23.840
Those who lay down their arms and surrender

24:23.960 --> 24:25.000
will be spared.

24:25.880 --> 24:27.200
Those who resist

24:27.720 --> 24:29.380
will be charged with treason,

24:30.240 --> 24:32.300
and their entire families executed.

24:33.750 --> 24:34.680
Prime Minister,

24:35.680 --> 24:37.480
you have been utterly defeated.

24:37.680 --> 24:39.480
Do you still intend to struggle?

24:43.070 --> 24:43.960
Jiuheng.

24:45.960 --> 24:47.880
You really didn't disappoint me.

24:51.640 --> 24:52.570
Prime Minister!

24:54.720 --> 24:55.580
Let's retreat.

24:55.960 --> 24:57.360
We'll get you out of here.

25:02.160 --> 25:03.190
No need.

25:06.070 --> 25:07.110
A defeat

25:08.070 --> 25:09.160
is a defeat.

25:09.840 --> 25:12.680
When I chose this path
of no return 17 years ago,

25:14.310 --> 25:15.590
today's outcome

25:17.550 --> 25:19.060
was already destined.

25:27.770 --> 25:28.570
Take him away.

25:30.830 --> 25:32.290
Let's go, Prime Minister.

26:05.680 --> 26:06.510
It's over.

26:10.480 --> 26:11.510
All of this

26:14.240 --> 26:15.480
is finally over.

26:18.710 --> 26:19.670
It's over.

26:23.270 --> 26:33.220
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

26:23.590 --> 26:25.590
Our lives will be better from now on.

26:29.510 --> 26:30.830
If there is a next life,

26:32.720 --> 26:34.060
I'll pick you up instead.

26:34.060 --> 26:43.610
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

26:44.630 --> 26:49.290
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

26:49.310 --> 26:53.980
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

26:54.850 --> 26:56.940
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

26:57.460 --> 27:02.070
♪ I find her there ♪

27:02.540 --> 27:12.230
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

27:12.380 --> 27:16.200
[Three days later]

27:31.880 --> 27:32.400
My Lord,

27:32.600 --> 27:33.600
Madam Wei is here.

27:35.200 --> 27:35.820
Madam,

27:35.880 --> 27:36.400
please.

27:42.310 --> 27:43.070
Aunt.

27:45.310 --> 27:46.160
Zheng.

27:50.310 --> 27:50.960
Aunt.

27:52.120 --> 27:54.120
What are you doing? Please get up.

27:54.640 --> 27:55.440
Zheng,

27:56.310 --> 27:58.120
I want to beg you

27:58.210 --> 28:00.210
to spare the Prime Minister's life.

28:05.550 --> 28:06.410
Sit down first.

28:12.190 --> 28:12.950
Aunt,

28:14.620 --> 28:16.830
he didn't even care about
the lives of you and your son.

28:16.830 --> 28:18.510
Why plead for him?

28:19.240 --> 28:21.510
Besides, the law will not permit it.

28:24.000 --> 28:26.880
The Prime Minister is not irredeemable.

28:28.310 --> 28:29.590
If not for him,

28:30.160 --> 28:31.310
Xuan and I

28:31.790 --> 28:33.190
would have died long ago.

28:35.590 --> 28:36.590
What do you mean?

28:37.790 --> 28:39.070
Xuan's father

28:39.830 --> 28:42.030
was the Prime Minister's subordinate.

28:42.790 --> 28:45.510
We pledged our lives to each other in secret.

28:46.510 --> 28:48.640
But he died in battle.

28:50.000 --> 28:51.220
My family

28:51.310 --> 28:53.270
wanted to drown me in a pig cage.

28:54.750 --> 28:56.880
It was the Prime Minister who saved me.

28:58.790 --> 28:59.880
He said

29:00.510 --> 29:03.410
Xuan's father was his former subordinate.

29:04.310 --> 29:07.720
He had no plans to marry in this life,

29:08.680 --> 29:10.950
but his family was pressuring him.

29:11.720 --> 29:14.570
Meanwhile, my unborn child and I

29:14.640 --> 29:16.310
had nowhere else to turn to.

29:17.270 --> 29:19.400
He said it was a win-win solution.

29:23.270 --> 29:25.920
To us,

29:27.680 --> 29:29.160
he is our saviour.

29:31.350 --> 29:32.110
Zheng.

29:33.030 --> 29:34.590
I beg you, for the sake of Xuan

29:34.590 --> 29:36.160
taking an arrow for you,

29:36.640 --> 29:38.900
please spare the Prime Minister's life.

29:43.000 --> 29:43.750
Aunt.

29:44.960 --> 29:46.290
Did he remain unmarried

29:47.110 --> 29:48.750
for Consort Virtue, Lady Qi?

29:52.570 --> 29:54.770
The Prime Minister is a shrewd man.

29:55.590 --> 29:57.320
I do not know of his intentions.

30:19.310 --> 30:20.160
Zheng.

30:21.680 --> 30:23.770
If the law truly cannot tolerate him,

30:24.160 --> 30:27.400
I beg you, for the sake of your bond
as uncle and nephew,

30:29.320 --> 30:31.400
please leave his body intact.

30:44.400 --> 30:46.790
The Flower-Crowned General has arrived.

30:52.300 --> 30:55.760
[Qionghua]

30:54.160 --> 30:54.880
Changyu.

30:56.400 --> 30:57.060
How are you?

30:57.440 --> 30:58.500
How is your injury?

30:58.920 --> 30:59.720
I'm fine.

30:59.900 --> 31:02.250
[Qionghua]

31:00.310 --> 31:01.030
Come here.

31:02.750 --> 31:03.680
Mother Consort.

31:05.400 --> 31:06.350
Your Highness.

31:10.000 --> 31:10.930
Mother Consort.

31:14.110 --> 31:15.570
Wei Yan has been captured.

31:16.590 --> 31:17.990
My brother has gone dumb.

31:19.030 --> 31:20.480
The world has shifted.

31:21.160 --> 31:22.510
What's the point of you

31:23.270 --> 31:24.600
still hiding the truth?

31:28.270 --> 31:29.930
The world has indeed shifted.

31:30.880 --> 31:32.270
It has already shifted

31:32.680 --> 31:33.960
17 years ago.

31:36.510 --> 31:39.110
When Consort Virtue first entered the palace,

31:39.640 --> 31:41.680
she was a very aloof person.

31:42.520 --> 31:44.890
She never vied for His Majesty's favor.

31:42.880 --> 31:45.380
[Late Emperor, Qi Yi]

31:46.110 --> 31:48.040
Then, she was found to be pregnant.

31:48.750 --> 31:51.790
The month of pregnancy determined
by the royal physician

31:51.790 --> 31:55.190
did not match the records of
the Department of State Affairs.

31:58.430 --> 32:01.430
Did Consort Virtue really have
an affair with Wei Yan?

32:01.450 --> 32:03.540
Qi Rongyin was 3 months pregnant.

32:04.070 --> 32:05.440
Counting back the days,

32:06.590 --> 32:09.920
she must have conceived it
around the Mid-Autumn Festival.

32:09.930 --> 32:11.990
At the Mid-Autumn banquet that year,

32:13.080 --> 32:15.300
Wei Yan got drunk at the palace banquet.

32:16.200 --> 32:17.550
He lost his propriety after drinking

32:17.550 --> 32:19.240
and defiled a palace maid.

32:20.030 --> 32:22.030
Unfortunately, the Late Emperor
and his officials caught him

32:22.030 --> 32:24.290
in the act on their way to admire the moon.

32:26.400 --> 32:28.440
She was just a lowly palace maid,

32:29.510 --> 32:32.510
so the Late Emperor could not
make a scene right there.

32:33.000 --> 32:36.110
He simply bestowed that maid upon Wei Yan.

32:37.550 --> 32:39.280
The royal family is heartless.

32:40.240 --> 32:42.840
After Consort Virtue was found to be pregnant,

32:43.720 --> 32:45.650
she was interrogated every night.

32:46.310 --> 32:48.310
Until the night of the Laba Festival,

32:48.310 --> 32:50.910
when Qingyuan Palace suddenly caught fire...

32:51.590 --> 32:52.070
Lord Wei? You-

32:52.070 --> 32:53.680
The Imperial Guard on patrol

32:53.790 --> 32:55.110
rushed to put out the fire,

32:54.560 --> 32:59.330
[Qingyuan Palace]

32:56.070 --> 32:57.670
only to discover that Wei Yan

32:57.850 --> 33:00.000
had entered the Capital without a decree

33:00.000 --> 33:02.110
and appeared in the Forbidden Palace.

33:02.110 --> 33:02.720
Scram!

33:02.920 --> 33:04.420
Zhao Xun once confessed

33:05.480 --> 33:08.540
that the palace fire was set
by Crown Princess Chengde.

33:09.200 --> 33:11.200
Is there a hidden story behind this?

33:12.270 --> 33:15.790
Have you ever seen water thrown into a fire

33:16.310 --> 33:18.170
make the flames leap even higher?

33:18.830 --> 33:20.260
I have.

33:20.590 --> 33:22.990
That fire reeked of tung oil.

33:23.590 --> 33:24.940
The palace city was besieged.

33:23.980 --> 33:26.550
[Qingyuan Palace]

33:25.000 --> 33:27.330
The sounds of fighting shook the heavens.

33:27.640 --> 33:29.640
Just like the day before yesterday.

33:30.920 --> 33:33.510
Later, the attending royal physician
committed suicide.

33:33.510 --> 33:35.110
He left a suicide note saying

33:35.110 --> 33:37.710
that Consort Virtue
was never pregnant at all.

33:37.790 --> 33:38.780
So,

33:39.030 --> 33:41.400
the one who set the fire
was Crown Princess Chengde,

33:41.400 --> 33:43.880
but the one who burned
Consort Virtue to death

33:43.880 --> 33:45.080
was the Late Emperor.

33:54.310 --> 33:55.770
Thank you, Your Highness,

33:56.350 --> 33:58.010
for telling me about the past.

34:31.880 --> 34:35.190
Jiuheng, are you here to see your uncle off?

34:36.800 --> 34:38.600
It's me. I've come to finish

34:38.840 --> 34:41.510
that unfinished game of chess with you.

34:46.270 --> 34:50.620
The brat's father, General Xie,
died tragically in Jinzhou.

34:50.800 --> 34:52.440
Regarding what happened back then,

34:52.440 --> 34:54.880
he is determined to get an answer.

34:59.590 --> 35:01.940
It was clearly the Late Emperor's setup.

35:02.070 --> 35:05.400
Why are you bearing
the infamy for a lifetime instead?

35:05.400 --> 35:06.930
What are you hoping to gain?

35:20.880 --> 35:21.970
I believe

35:23.030 --> 35:25.560
this chess formation is most familiar to you.

35:52.280 --> 35:53.550
Have you made up your mind?

35:53.550 --> 35:54.650
If not,

35:55.230 --> 35:56.630
let me take another nap.

35:58.150 --> 35:58.920
Yan.

35:59.400 --> 36:00.400
You're cheating.

36:01.000 --> 36:03.460
You promised to use only 30% of your skill.

36:03.920 --> 36:05.070
But clearly,

36:05.670 --> 36:07.630
you're going all out to corner me.

36:07.630 --> 36:10.490
I really am only using 30%.

36:10.590 --> 36:11.960
Then just admit that

36:12.480 --> 36:13.630
I'm bad at chess

36:13.760 --> 36:14.820
and can't beat you.

36:15.760 --> 36:16.630
I'm done.

36:18.920 --> 36:20.920
Fine. I'll make a different move.

36:21.760 --> 36:23.230
Let me think about

36:23.250 --> 36:26.980
how to lose gracefully with 30% skill.

36:30.480 --> 36:31.870
It's not hard to lose.

36:31.960 --> 36:33.550
Let me help you, Brother.

36:33.550 --> 36:35.210
Sister, stop messing around.

36:35.510 --> 36:37.510
Brother, you blockhead.

36:37.510 --> 36:40.240
Win again, and you'll scare
Sister-in-law away.

36:42.590 --> 36:44.630
Wan'er said you were playing chess here.

36:44.630 --> 36:47.190
I thought I'd join in the fun.

36:47.760 --> 36:48.920
No need for ceremony.

36:48.920 --> 36:50.480
Sit. Please sit.

36:55.590 --> 36:58.870
If a piece becomes isolated and helpless,

36:59.230 --> 37:02.260
you must quickly find a way to revitalize it.

37:11.840 --> 37:14.030
Chess is like life.

37:14.550 --> 37:16.400
One must sacrifice to gain.

37:19.070 --> 37:20.550
Chess is like life.

37:21.230 --> 37:22.760
One must sacrifice to gain.

37:24.920 --> 37:25.710
Grand Tutor,

37:26.250 --> 37:27.640
those were your words.

37:29.000 --> 37:30.360
At this point,

37:31.590 --> 37:33.860
stop speaking in riddles.

37:34.280 --> 37:35.670
I never believed

37:36.230 --> 37:38.670
that you planned the Jinzhou Massacre.

37:39.730 --> 37:42.990
But why did you return to the Capital
so abruptly back then?

37:44.360 --> 37:46.070
What exactly happened?

37:47.590 --> 37:50.510
Do you remember the osmanthus wine banquet

37:51.710 --> 37:54.570
at the Eastern Palace on
New Year's Eve 18 years ago?

37:55.760 --> 37:56.550
Grand Tutor,

37:56.960 --> 37:58.590
you were there too.

38:00.480 --> 38:01.360
That night,

38:01.710 --> 38:03.460
I was young and arrogant,

38:04.510 --> 38:06.800
and my words sowed the seeds of disaster.

38:06.910 --> 38:14.660
[The 25th year of Taikang]

38:15.510 --> 38:16.850
Today is New Year's Eve.

38:17.230 --> 38:18.530
I invited you all here

38:18.630 --> 38:22.260
to taste the Eastern Palace's
homemade osmanthus wine.

38:22.440 --> 38:23.890
Fine wine in winter,

38:22.540 --> 38:26.250
[Crown Prince Chengde, Qi Yuan]

38:24.000 --> 38:25.660
paired with roasted venison,

38:25.710 --> 38:26.920
isn't it delightful?

38:27.960 --> 38:31.250
[Libationer of the Imperial Academy, Li Xing]
[Minister of the Two Ministries, Tao Yi]

38:28.670 --> 38:29.270
Thank you.

38:30.070 --> 38:31.200
This osmanthus wine

38:31.760 --> 38:32.880
is incredibly fragrant.

38:32.200 --> 38:36.260
[General Wei Yan]
[General Protector Xie Linshan]

38:33.400 --> 38:34.190
It is truly a fine brew.

38:34.190 --> 38:35.510
Here, Your Highness.

38:35.670 --> 38:36.930
Let me toast you again.

38:36.960 --> 38:37.800
General Xie.

38:38.480 --> 38:40.380
Did you get permission today

38:40.440 --> 38:42.300
to drink to your heart's content?

38:42.400 --> 38:44.530
I advise you to drink less.

38:44.770 --> 38:46.150
Save some for the rest of us

38:46.150 --> 38:47.840
to have a taste, won't you?

38:48.760 --> 38:50.710
General Wei is right.

38:51.400 --> 38:53.400
Linshan, you have a high tolerance.

38:53.480 --> 38:55.190
If you don't restrain yourself,

38:55.190 --> 38:57.440
there will be none left for us.

38:57.590 --> 38:58.320
You...

38:58.480 --> 38:59.210
Grand Tutor,

38:59.590 --> 39:01.520
it's just osmanthus wine.

39:01.630 --> 39:03.030
As long as you all like it,

39:03.480 --> 39:04.410
there is plenty.

39:04.840 --> 39:05.510
Good.

39:06.510 --> 39:08.150
-Let’s drink.
-We'll have our share.

39:08.150 --> 39:09.320
-Come on.
-Come on.

39:11.960 --> 39:13.550
Fine wine, good food,

39:13.630 --> 39:15.110
loyal subjects, a wise ruler,

39:15.110 --> 39:16.550
and the company of close friends.

39:16.550 --> 39:19.150
These are the greatest joys in life.

39:19.150 --> 39:20.150
Qilin, my friend.

39:20.480 --> 39:22.810
This might be the last time

39:22.920 --> 39:24.350
we stay up for New Year's Eve together.

39:24.350 --> 39:27.840
[General Discipline Inspector, He Jingyuan]

39:24.630 --> 39:26.290
I am about to leave the Capital

39:27.110 --> 39:28.190
for Jinzhou.

39:28.560 --> 39:31.500
[Huaihua General Wei Qilin]

39:28.670 --> 39:29.480
He,

39:30.280 --> 39:31.800
the Northwest Frontier is desolate.

39:31.800 --> 39:34.880
Jinzhou, Chongzhou, and Jizhou
are especially barren.

39:34.880 --> 39:37.280
You must take care of yourself
on this trip.

39:37.960 --> 39:40.670
A good man should establish himself.

39:41.150 --> 39:43.070
It is better than being in the Capital,

39:43.070 --> 39:46.510
bowing and scraping to the powerful.

39:48.180 --> 39:48.950
What a pity.

39:49.510 --> 39:51.710
I won't be there for my nephew's birth.

39:51.710 --> 39:52.760
Niece.

39:53.320 --> 39:54.580
You prefer daughters?

39:56.110 --> 39:58.630
He, you're more well-read than I am.

39:58.760 --> 40:00.440
Give your niece a name.

40:00.760 --> 40:04.530
Why don't you let your Lord name her?

40:04.670 --> 40:06.400
General Wei's rank is too high.

40:06.480 --> 40:08.680
I fear the child can't bear such weight.

40:09.360 --> 40:10.420
Grand Libationer,

40:10.710 --> 40:13.280
my Jiuheng is quite smart.

40:13.280 --> 40:16.230
When can he go to your Imperial Academy

40:16.710 --> 40:18.280
to study?

40:19.400 --> 40:20.960
Xie Zheng is still a child.

40:21.760 --> 40:23.070
You are his uncle.

40:23.190 --> 40:25.520
His own father isn't even anxious.

40:25.920 --> 40:27.320
Who says I'm not anxious?

40:27.360 --> 40:28.280
You have no idea.

40:28.280 --> 40:30.280
That little rascal is a terror.

40:30.280 --> 40:32.010
He causes trouble all day long.

40:32.030 --> 40:32.710
I'm not kidding.

40:32.710 --> 40:34.440
I want to send him
to the Imperial Academy right now

40:34.440 --> 40:36.440
so you can discipline him properly.

40:40.150 --> 40:41.190
Changyu.

40:41.510 --> 40:42.480
Changyu?

40:42.480 --> 40:43.070
Yes.

40:43.920 --> 40:45.190
Wei Changyu.

40:45.360 --> 40:46.710
"Chang," as in "Long may I stay
by your side,"

40:46.710 --> 40:48.440
and "yu," as in "Where jade steps bloom
with springtide."

40:48.440 --> 40:49.760
What do you think?

40:50.840 --> 40:51.900
That is a fine name.

40:52.440 --> 40:54.880
Later, I'll bring your niece to greet you.

40:59.800 --> 41:00.960
Good wine.

41:01.190 --> 41:04.510
-Next year, General will lead troops to guard Jinzhou.
-Good wine.

41:04.510 --> 41:06.240
If the General does not object,

41:06.550 --> 41:07.810
I wish to go with you...

41:10.590 --> 41:12.790
And face the national crisis together.

41:15.020 --> 41:16.380
Your Highness's safety

41:16.630 --> 41:19.880
concerns the stability
of the court and the state.

41:19.880 --> 41:21.480
We cannot be rash.

41:22.280 --> 41:23.110
Indeed.

41:23.760 --> 41:26.090
A noble son must not sit under a leaky roof.

41:27.030 --> 41:29.030
Please reconsider, Your Highness.

41:29.280 --> 41:31.210
There is something you do not know.

41:31.590 --> 41:33.990
There were floods in the south this summer.

41:34.320 --> 41:36.110
I went to provide disaster relief.

41:36.110 --> 41:38.230
But the Jia family obstructed me at every turn.

41:38.230 --> 41:40.480
The victims suffered unspeakably.

41:41.070 --> 41:42.330
My father was furious.

41:43.440 --> 41:44.570
But he did not pursue

41:45.190 --> 41:48.190
the faults of the Sixteenth Prince
and the Jia family.

41:48.230 --> 41:49.430
Instead, he blamed me

41:50.800 --> 41:52.660
for ineffective relief efforts.

41:54.030 --> 41:55.230
Over these years,

41:55.670 --> 41:58.710
Father has been especially harsh on me,

41:59.670 --> 42:02.600
while being more than lenient
towards the Jia family

42:03.360 --> 42:04.820
and the Sixteenth Prince.

42:05.840 --> 42:07.590
I am lost.

42:09.110 --> 42:10.150
Perhaps,

42:10.550 --> 42:12.640
only by staying away from the court

42:14.230 --> 42:16.090
and achieving merit at the border

42:17.190 --> 42:20.030
can I find

42:20.710 --> 42:22.150
my ultimate path.

42:32.230 --> 42:33.800
These family trifles...

42:36.550 --> 42:38.010
I have made a fool of myself

42:40.000 --> 42:41.190
in front of you all.

42:43.360 --> 42:45.760
Your Highness, you possess
both benevolence and virtue.

42:45.760 --> 42:47.480
You are wise and brave.

42:47.920 --> 42:50.150
You are the only choice
to succeed to the throne.

42:50.150 --> 42:51.030
I just don't understand

42:51.030 --> 42:53.550
why His Majesty is so biased.

42:59.360 --> 43:01.510
If the Emperor lacks virtue,

43:05.360 --> 43:07.400
then simply have him abdicate.
